The paper deals with the problem of preventing malicious calls over telephony networks using machine learning. This problem falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR), which is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves the use of machine learning algorithms (cs.AI) and the design of features based on a measurement study (cs.SI). Additionally, the paper deals with network infrastructures (cs.NI) and evaluates the efficiency of the proposed models (cs.LG).
